{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Co-Op Gameplay Experience</h2>Explore, drill, and produce oil on your own or team up with up to five friends. Work together for faster progress and make strategic decisions to run a successful operation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Oil Exploration and Extraction</h2>Lease land from the municipality to search for oil. Extract crude oil and transport it to your storage facilities using barrels or tanker trucks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441460/extras/store1.gif?t=1739265565\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Item Production and Market Sales</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Process crude oil into petroleum products using industrial machinery, then set your own prices and sell them in your shop.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441460/extras/store2.gif?t=1739265565\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Fuel Production and Sales</h2>Refine crude oil into a variety of fuels such as diesel and gasoline. Negotiate with gas stations to sell your products and maximize your profits.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Valuable Discoveries</h2>During excavations, you\u2019ll uncover not only oil but also precious gems, fossils, and minerals. Add them to your collection and earn extra revenue.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441460/extras/store3.gif?t=1739265565\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Equipment Upgrades</h2>Enhance everything from your detectors and vehicles to your oil pumps. Expand your brand and grow your factory to increase efficiency and output.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Ultimate Goal: Become the City\u2019s Leading Oil Supplier</h2>As you earn more money, unlock new regions, acquire larger equipment, and aim to become the sole provider of oil that powers the entire city.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441460/extras/store4.gif?t=1739265565\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Additional Side Mechanics</h2>Keep an eye on the stock market, engage in e-commerce, and discover surprise mechanics for endless new opportunities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Get ready for a strategic, cooperative, and exploratory adventure!</strong></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3441460?t=1739265565","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441460/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1739265565","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441460/261b59651cb089366f1939f7864e12b5a943850c/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739265565","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441460/261b59651cb089366f1939f7864e12b5a943850c/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739265565","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Online Co-op","id":38},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<h1>Add To Wishlist</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441460/extras/wishlist.gif?t=1739265565\" /></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Co-Op Gameplay Experience</h2>Explore, drill, and produce oil on your own or team up with up to five friends. Work together for faster progress and make strategic decisions to run a successful operation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Oil Exploration and Extraction</h2>Lease land from the municipality to search for oil. Extract crude oil and transport it to your storage facilities using barrels or tanker trucks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441460/extras/store1.gif?t=1739265565\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Item Production and Market Sales</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Process crude oil into petroleum products using industrial machinery, then set your own prices and sell them in your shop.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441460/extras/store2.gif?t=1739265565\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Fuel Production and Sales</h2>Refine crude oil into a variety of fuels such as diesel and gasoline. Negotiate with gas stations to sell your products and maximize your profits.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Valuable Discoveries</h2>During excavations, you\u2019ll uncover not only oil but also precious gems, fossils, and minerals. Add them to your collection and earn extra revenue.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441460/extras/store3.gif?t=1739265565\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Equipment Upgrades</h2>Enhance everything from your detectors and vehicles to your oil pumps. Expand your brand and grow your factory to increase efficiency and output.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Ultimate Goal: Become the City\u2019s Leading Oil Supplier</h2>As you earn more money, unlock new regions, acquire larger equipment, and aim to become the sole provider of oil that powers the entire city.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441460/extras/store4.gif?t=1739265565\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Additional Side Mechanics</h2>Keep an eye on the stock market, engage in e-commerce, and discover surprise mechanics for endless new opportunities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Get ready for a strategic, cooperative, and exploratory adventure!</strong></p>","developers":["Grejuva"],"genres":[{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"Simulation","id":"28"},{"description":"Early Access","id":"70"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441460/header.jpg?t=1739265565","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257090919,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257090919/movie480.mp4?t=1737738346","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257090919/movie_max.mp4?t=1737738346"},"name":"Fuel Harvest Together Gameplay Trailer","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/257090919/c50f15e47ed5dc127a97c4e91e92e7204eaee14b/movie_600x337.jpg?t=1737738346","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257090919/movie480_vp9.webm?t=1737738346","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257090919/movie_max_vp9.webm?t=1737738346"}}],"name":"Fuel Harvest Together","package_groups":[],"pc_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS:</strong> Windows (64-bit) 10<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> Intel Core i5-2500 @ 3,3 GHz (4 CPUs)<br></li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 8 GB RAM<br></li><li><strong>Graphics:</strong> NVidia GeForce GTX 1050<br></li><li><strong>Direc